26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_engine_disp_rootgk110.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:31 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "rootnv50.h"
30#include "dmacnv50.h"
31
32#include <nvif/class.h>
33
34static const struct nv50_disp_root_func
35gk110_disp_root = {
36 .init = gf119_disp_root_init,
37 .fini = gf119_disp_root_fini,
38 .dmac = {
39 &gk110_disp_core_oclass,
40 &gk110_disp_base_oclass,
41 &gk104_disp_ovly_oclass,
42 },
43 .pioc = {
44 &gk104_disp_oimm_oclass,
45 &gk104_disp_curs_oclass,
46 },
47};
48
49static int
50gk110_disp_root_new(struct nvkm_disp *disp, const struct nvkm_oclass *oclass,
51 void *data, u32 size, struct nvkm_object **pobject)
52{
53 return nv50_disp_root_new_(&gk110_disp_root, disp, oclass,
54 data, size, pobject);
55}
56
57const struct nvkm_disp_oclass
58gk110_disp_root_oclass = {
59 .base.oclass = GK110_DISP,
60 .base.minver = -1,
61 .base.maxver = -1,
62 .ctor = gk110_disp_root_new,
63};
